        "text": "Hi @Bramm ,\n\nThis is Victor from PageFly - Landing page builder, I’d like to suggest this idea for solution:\n\nStep 1. Go to Online Store -> Theme -> Edit code\n\nStep 2. Open your theme.liquid theme file\n\nStep 3. Paste below code before </body> :\n\n<style> .product-block__title, .product-block__vendor, .product-block .product-price{ text-align: left; } .product-block__title { padding-top: 25px; min-height: auto !important; } .product-price { margin-top: unset !important } </style>\n\nHope my answer will help you.\n\nBest regards,\n\nVictor | PageFly\n\nHi @Bramm, you can do that by opening Sale channels > Online store > Themes > Edit code > Assets > open style.css or style.css.liquid file, add this CSS code at the bottom and save file\n\n.product-block { text-align: left !important; } .product-block .product-block__title { min-height: auto !important; }\n\nHere is the result\n\n- Helpful? Like and Accept solution! ‌Support me: Buy coffee\n\n- Ryviu - Reviews & QA app, collect product reviews, import reviews from AliExpress, Amazon, Etsy, Walmart, Shopee, Dhgate and CSV.\n\n- Lookfy app: Easy and fast to create Photo Gallery, Lookbook, Shop The Look.\n\n- Reelfy‑Shoppable Videos+Reels: Create shoppable videos to engage customers and drive more sales.\n\n- Enjoy 1 month of Shopify for $1. Sign up now."
